{"tid":1207201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［廣傳］現場急需整理行動組織","createTime":"2019-06-12T05:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T06:05:52.000Z","uid":128804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4677978c8a6c3c52f88ecbb39b7dc7c03a6f14fd","tid":1207201,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:32:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推佢上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今次行動嘅組織仍然非常鬆散<br />\n當年台灣太陽花學運之所以成功,係因為佢哋可以迅速形成有效嘅行動組織網<br />\n我哋都要做到一樣嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係各小組嘅分組同主要職責<br />\n請大家幫手補充<br />\n<br />\n1. 物資組<br />\n主要職責:<br />\n建立物資站<br />\n集中,搬運及分派物資<br />\n將每日需要嘅物資項目發佈至網上<br />\n<br />\n2. 救護站<br />\n主要職責:<br />\n現場急救<br />\n組織救傷小組,分散至各區待命<br />\n集中醫療用物資<br />\n<br />\n3. 文宣組<br />\n主要職責:<br />\n起草行動宣言<br />\n繪製地圖,標示各救護站,物資站的位置<br />\n對外統一發佈行動消息<br />\n<br />\n4. 訊息/哨兵組<br />\n主要職責:<br />\n建立訊息網絡<br />\n接收第一手消息,分析消息來源及其可信度<br />\n將已確認資訊傳到分佈於各區嘅訊息小組<br />\n<br />\n5. 行動核心決策組<br />\n組成方法:<br />\n由各小組選出一名組長作為當然組員<br />\n再加入學生領袖,立法會議員等人自薦加入<br />\n<br />\n主要職責:<br />\n選出行動精神領袖<br />\n協調各小組的工作<br />\n組織突發行動<br />\n帶頭行動<br />\n決定今次運動嘅主要訴求<br />\n與政府展開談判<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有組織都需要有:<br />\n一個名,ex. 612 文宣組<br />\n一個leader<br />\n同埋一啲可以比大家認出嘅記認,例如將白布條扣係衫袖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知大家都好討厭大台<br />\n但我哋一定要有一個完善組織先有得贏<br />\n如果各位嚟到現場,請務必到現場幫手<br />\n<br />\n求求大家,今次一定要齊心<br />\n<br />\n補充閱讀:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5056813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cw.com.tw%2Farticle%2Farticle.action%3Fid%3D5056813&d=Upau0OFRhNBgg6kYd6CVywbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=c910ecfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5056813</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E8%8A%B1%E5%AD%B8%E9%81%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E9%2599%25BD%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E9%2581%258B&d=Upau0OFRhNBgg6kYd6CVywbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=7d03eac5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E8%8A%B1%E5%AD%B8%E9%81%8B</a>"},{"pid":"7b7508ab7bf36749efba51271104d01f2e09533b","tid":1207201,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"a367d0cbc7c65119822fd0937e64031318a6e9b8","tid":1207201,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"1665f22ad50af865f418473acfdb018302de109c","tid":1207201,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:36:02.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"641725a2640813090ced9ad46bb82baacb2d3ee3","tid":1207201,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:36:12.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"fcba36ada099dd8fc705ee6f3c1244249bac71e7","tid":1207201,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"e2abf5b7e829927faf2a9767b19c243890707c56","tid":1207201,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"52e9c71216b01ffbd85ff7baca85db93e718797b","tid":1207201,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"192470c74616c6de3ac35e462685e445967229f2","tid":1207201,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:37:42.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"d1ff1d7e784f0e82b0ee6b8a83849a45c7d6edea","tid":1207201,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:38:13.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"2386f39bb7533d413d1114f8912e8bb02dc3e708","tid":1207201,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:39:21.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pi